    <item>
      <title>工党有望获胜，富时 100 指数期货上涨，英镑持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国出口民调显示工党将确保其长期预测的压倒性选举胜利，而基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 有望凭借更大的经济稳定承诺成为首相，英国股票期货随之上涨，英镑保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/pound-steady-as-labour-projected-to-win-majority-in-uk-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 21:08:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铃木启动 4000 万美元印度基金，助力农村初创企业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/suzuki-starts-40-million-fund-in-india-to-help-rural-startups</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铃木汽车公司在印度推出了一只 4000 万美元的基金，用于投资印度农村小型企业，这家日本汽车制造商旨在提升其在印度这个世界增长最快的市场之一的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/suzuki-starts-40-million-fund-in-india-to-help-rural-startups</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 06:11:32 GMT</pubDate>
